    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but it doesn't feel like a chapter. chapters end and new ones begin, but this feels like the book is just... finished. i keep trying to wait for the \"healing\" you're talking about, but what if there's nothing left to heal? if the soul of the work is dead, what am i even doing here? just occupying space? it feels so pointless to keep dragging this empty shell around.",
